# UI

The UI must never jump.

Prevent layout shifts.

Skeletons must match the final layout exactly.

Loading states should mirror real content.

Buttons should disable while submitting.

Prevent double taps.

Show meaningful empty states.

Show meaningful error states.

Animations should be subtle.

Accessibility is required.

Support dark mode.

Respect safe areas.

Keep interactions under 100ms whenever possible.
